abstract: >-
  Research on format friction in LLM tool-calling systems.
  We find a 10.3pp gap between signal detection and XML compliance,
  with friction concentrating in ambiguous scenarios (0pp explicit vs 18.4pp implicit).
  Two-pass recovery mechanisms can recover 50-74% of compliance gaps.
